<xref type="reprint from" targOrder="U" from="ROOT" to="DITTO" n="psi;4;435" evaluate="all">SB3,6713;PEdg7;PSI4,435</xref></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἀπολλωνίωι χαίρειν Ζωίλος Ἀ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σπέν</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">δ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ιο</unclear>ς τ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ῶν </supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="2"/>ὃς καὶ διασυνεστάθη σοι ὑπὸ τῶν τοῦ βασιλέως φίλων. ἐμοὶ σ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">υμ</unclear>βέβηκεν 

    <lb n="3"/>θεραπεύοντι τὸν θεὸν Σάραπιν περὶ τῆς σῆς ὑγιείας καὶ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">εὐ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">η</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">μερία</unclear>ς τῆς 

    <lb n="4"/>πρὸς <choice><corr>τὸν</corr><sic>τομ</sic></choice> βασιλέα Πτολεμαῖον τὸν <choice><corr>Σάραπίν</corr><sic>σαραπιμ</sic></choice> μοι χρημα<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τίζει</supplied>ν <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">π</unclear>λε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">νάκι</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς</supplied> 

    <lb n="5"/>ἐν τοῖς ὕπνοις, ὅπως ἂν διαπλεύσω π<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρὸς</unclear> σὲ κ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">αὶ</unclear> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ανίσω σοι τό</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">νδε</unclear> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied> 

    <lb n="6"/>χρηματισμόν, ὅτι δεῖ συντελεσθῆναι αὐτ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ῶι</unclear> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="7"/>καὶ τέμενος ἐν τῆι Ἑλληνικῆι πρὸς τῶι λιμέν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κα</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὶ</supplied> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἱ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ερέα</supplied> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἐπιστ</unclear>ατεῖν <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αὶ</supplied> 

    <lb n="8"/>ἐπιβωμίζειν ὑπὲρ ὑμῶν. ἐμοῦ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δὲ</unclear> π<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αιτησαμένου </supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="9"/>ὅπως <choice><corr>ἄν</corr><sic>αμ</sic></choice> με παραλύσηι τοῦ ἐνταῦθ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἔργο</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">υ</unclear>, εἰς <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἀρρωσ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ία</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">μ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε πε</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ριέβα</unclear>λεν 

    <lb n="10"/>μεγάλην ὥστε καὶ κινδυνεῦσ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">αί</unclear> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">με</supplied>· <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">προ</unclear>σευξάμενος δ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὲ</supplied> αὐ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τῶι, ἐ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ά</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν με</supplied> 

    <lb n="11"/>ὑγιάσηι, διότι ὑπομενῶ τὴν <choice><corr>λειτουργίαν</corr><sic>ληιτο<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">υρ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">γ</unclear>ιαν</sic></choice> καὶ ποι<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ή</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σει</supplied>ν <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τὸ</unclear> ὑφ᾽ αὑτοῦ 

    <lb n="12"/>προστασσόμενον. ἐπεὶ δὲ τάχιστα ὑγιά<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σθ</unclear>ην, 

παρεγένετό τις ἐκ Κνίδου 

    <lb n="13"/>ὃς ἐνεχείρησεν οἰκοδομεῖν Σαραπιεῖον ἐν τῶι τόπωι τούτωι καὶ προσ-

    <lb n="14"/>αγηγόχει λίθους· ὕστερον δὲ ἀπεῖπεν αὐτῶι ὁ θεὸς μὴ οἰκοδομεῖν, καὶ <choice><corr>ἐκεῖνος</corr><sic>κακεινος</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="15"/>ἀπηλλάγη. ἐμοῦ δὲ παραγενομένου εἰς Ἀλεξάνδρειαν καὶ ὀκνοῦντός σοι 

    <lb n="16"/>περὶ τούτων ἐντυχεῖν, ἀλλὰ περὶ πραγματείας ἧς καὶ ὡμολογήκεις μοι, 

    <lb n="17"/>πάλιν ὑπετροπάσθην μῆνας τέσσερας <num value="4"/>· διὸ οὐκ ἠδυνάμην εὐθέως παραγε-

    <lb n="18"/>νέσθαι πρὸς σέ. καλῶς οὖν ἔχει, Ἀπολλώνιε, ἐπακολουθῆσαί σε τοῖς ὑπὸ τοῦ 

    <lb n="19"/>θεοῦ προστάγμασιν, ὅπως ἂν εὐίλατός σοι ὑπάρχων ὁ Σάραπις πολλῶι σε 

    <lb n="20"/>μείζω παρὰ τῶι βασιλεῖ καὶ ἐνδοξότερον μετὰ τῆς τοῦ σώματος ὑγιείας 

    <lb n="21"/>ποιήσηι. <add place="supralinear">σὺ οὖν</add> μὴ καταπλαγῆις <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/></del> τὸ ἀνήλωμα ὡς ἀπὸ μεγάλης σοι δαπάνης 

    <lb n="22"/>ἐσομένης, ἀλλ᾽ ἔσται σοι ἀπὸ πάνυ λυσιτελοῦντος· συνεπιστατήσω γὰρ ἐγὼ πᾶ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σι</unclear> 

    <lb n="23"/>τούτοις. 

    <lb n="24"/>εὐτύχει. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="25"/>Ζωίλου περὶ Σαράπιος. 

    <lb n="26"/><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="28">κη</num>, Αὐδναίου <num value="9">θ</num>, 

    <lb n="27"/>ἐν τῶι Βερενίκης 

    <lb n="28"/>ὅρμωι. 

    <lb n="25"/>Ἀπολλωνίωι. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.694" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.694" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notAfter="-0257-02-13">vor 13. Febr. 257 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.694" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Vgl. GRBS 41, 2001, S. 117-124.</p></div><div n="meta.694" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>verso Z. 2: <date type="mentioned" value="-0257-02-13">13. Febr. 257 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.694" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59034</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">694</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59034</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0092;1;59034" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.694" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">77</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">49</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">36</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.694